      <description>The XSitePro software program by Paul Smithson just so happens to be one of the easiest to use web design tools available, and it was exclusively created with Internet marketers in mind. When there were already solutions on the market, why did Paul decide to build this software? The answer is: weakness. He realized that [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/digireviewer-digital-product-reviews/DigiReviewer_-_Digital_Product_Reviews-XSitePro_Review.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://www.digireviewer.com/xsitepro" target="_blank" rel="nofollow"><img src="http://www.digireviewer.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/xsitepro-review.jpg" alt="XSitePro Review" border="0" width="200" height="147" style="float:left;" /></a>The <em><a href="http://www.digireviewer.com/xsitepro" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">XSitePro</a></em> software program by Paul Smithson just so happens to be one of the easiest to use web design tools available, and it was exclusively created with Internet marketers in mind.</p>
<p>When there were already solutions on the market, why did Paul decide to build this software? The answer is: weakness.</p>
<p>He realized that the other web design tools were very limited when it came to helping Internet marketers create SEO friendly sites that got great conversions. Any person using Dreamweaver would know there is a lot of time needed initially in creating a webpage, especially if you&#8217;re a rookie and are not real tech-savvy. This is literally what caused Paul to develop this software so that online marketers didn&#8217;t have to keep facing hurdles when making their web pages.<span id="more-403"></span></p>
<h3>Best XSitePro Software Features</h3>
<ul>
<li><strong>SEO Analysis Tool</strong> &#8211; This is one of those features that are worth the whole price. SEO is a very important part of any internet marketing campaign. This software has features that allow you to rank and analyze all of your websites for SEO&#8211;you won&#8217;t have to outsource it anymore. If you want good results fast, use this software to analyze any website for hints and tips on what needs to be changed and how you should change it to make it more SEO friendly. Your website&#8217;s ranking in the search engines depends upon the keywords you target and you can use the SEO Analysis Tool to learn what little changes you can make to ensure that your site ranks well for the keywords that you have picked out.</li>
<p></p>
<li><strong>Premium XSitePro Templates</strong> &#8211; The biggest concern Internet marketers have about their sites are the designs. You have a couple of choices in this: you can hire someone to design your template for you or you can buy something that has been premade. But when you&#8217;re using <a href="http://www.digireviewer.com/xsitepro" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">XSitePro</a> 2, you&#8217;ll be getting hundreds of high quality templates that come with the software. You can use these templates for enhancing or creating your sites from scratch. XSitePro 2 also comes with X Header, a tool that helps you create professional header graphics for your various websites. So you no longer need to worry about outsourcing your graphics work.</li>
</ul>
<h3>XSitePro Program Limitations</h3>
<p>So is XSitePro 2 deprived of anything? Well, no software is perfect, which is why this tool does have a few minor problems (they&#8217;re actually limitations).</p>
<p>For starters, if you are already quite knowledgeable about HTML coding, then you&#8217;ll probably think the code designed by XSitePro 2 is a bit in the wrong place. You do have a &#8220;source tab&#8221; that lets you edit the HTML but it&#8217;s kind of limited. This is how you&#8217;re limited when you&#8217;re using an automated web design software, but majority of the time, this won&#8217;t prove to be a problem. So if you absolutely desire to get the as much out of it as you can, you&#8217;ll have to overlook some of the weak points, because the overall benefit you get from the software is amazing.</p>
<h3>XSitePro Review &#8211; Conclusion</h3>
<p>The bottom line is, <strong><a href="http://www.digireviewer.com/xsitepro" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">XSitePro</a></strong> 2 is one of the best solutions for any Internet Marketer who wants to create basic SEO friendly websites that will help you sell more products and make more money.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
